        <num>CC 657</num>
        <heading>657.  Estate bordering on running water</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 657.  Estate bordering on running water.
The owner of an estate bordering on running water may use it as it runs for the purpose of watering his estate or for other purposes.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
